OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTV's Alastair Stewart      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freveals dementia diagnosis 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Alastair Stewart has revealed he is    
OL,6, living with dementia and has suffered a
OL,7, series of minor strokes, discovered    
OL,8, after he felt "discombobulated".       
OL,10,FThe broadcaster, 71, retired this year 
OL,11,Fafter nearly five decades on air.      
OL,13,FStewart, who previously worked for ITV 
OL,14,FNews and Channel 4, told GB News his   
OL,15,Fhealth was behind the decision to leave
OL,16,Fhis full-time role with the channel.   
OL,18,FHe hosted his final episode of Alastair
OL,19,FStewart And Friends, a discussion      
OL,20,Fprogramme on GB News, in March.        
